n=int(input('Enter your number:'))
t=n
sum=0
while(n>0):
    a=n%10
    sum=(sum*10)+a
    n=n//10
print('The Reverse of',t,'is:',sum)

Result:
-------
Ex1:
    Enter your number:1254
    The Reverse of 1254 is: 4521

Ex2:
    Enter your number:9856
    The Reverse of 9856 is: 6589

Ex3:
    Enter your number:45
    The Reverse of 45 is: 54

Ex4:
    Enter your number:781
    The Reverse of 781 is: 187
